          <h2>What Qualifies as an AC Emergency?</h2>
          <p>An AC emergency is any situation where the loss of cooling poses a risk to health, safety, or property:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Complete AC failure during extreme heat</li>
            <li>AC stopped working with elderly, infants, or medically vulnerable family members at home</li>
            <li>AC stopped working with pets that can't be relocated</li>
            <li>Burning smell or smoke from your AC system</li>
            <li>AC making loud, unusual noises before stopping</li>
            <li>Water flooding from your indoor AC unit</li>
            <li>AC tripping breaker repeatedly</li>
          </ul>

